a=input("enter a value") 
a=int(a) 
b=input("enter b value") 
b=int(b) 
c=input("enter c value") 
c=int(c) 
average=(a+b+c) /3
average=int(average) 
print('average of three numbers is:',average) 
total=a+b+c
print('the total of three numbers is:',total)

Output:
enter a value3
enter b value4
enter c value5
average of three numbers is: 4
the total of three numbers is: 12
